original_title: Adele: From 19 to 30 - In Her Own Words
overview: A look at the career of the singer ahead of the release of her new album 30, her first in six years, examining how she is able to retain such a loyal fan base after disappearing from the business for long periods. The movie explores Adele's latest press appearances, including two simultaneous Vogue covers after sitting for separate interviews and photo shoots for the magazine's US and UK editions
title: Adele: From 19 to 30 - In Her Own Words
